== Setup

At the terminal:
  git clone git://github.com/stouset/textmate-bundles.git ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
  cd ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
  git pull
  git clean -ffd
  git submodule sync
  git submodule update --init

In TextMate:
  Bundles -> Bundle Editor -> Reload Bundles

== Update

At the terminal:
  cd ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
  rake update

In TextMate:
  Bundles -> Bundle Editor -> Reload Bundles


